<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <style>


        .container7 {
            display: flex;
            margin: auto;
            gap: 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .contact-info {
            background-color: #161b22;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            flex: 1;
        }

            .contact-info h3 {
                margin-top: 0;
            }

            .contact-info p {
                margin: 0.5rem 0;
            }

        .contact-form {
            flex: 2;
            background-color: #161b22;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

            .contact-form h2 {
                margin-top: 0;
            }

            .contact-form form {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea, .contact-form select {
                padding: 0.75rem;
                border: 1px solid #333;
                border-radius: 4px;
                background-color: #0d1117;
                color: #ffffff;
            }

                .contact-form input:focus, .contact-form textarea:focus {
                    outline: none;
                    border-color: #yellow;
                }

            .contact-form button {
                padding: 0.75rem;
                background-color: #f1c40f;
                color: #0d1117;
                border: none;
                border-radius: 4px;
                cursor: pointer;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

                .contact-form button:hover {
                    background-color: #d4ac0d;
                }

            .contact-form textarea {
                resize: none;
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container7">
        <div class="contact-info">
            <h3>Chat with us</h3>
            <p>Our friendly team is here to help.</p>

            <h3>Visit us</h3>
            <p>Come and say hello at our office HQ. Here is the location/address.</p>

            <h3>Call us</h3>
            <p>Mon - Fri From 8am to 5pm. +123 456 7890</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-form">
            <h2>Got a Idea? We've got the skills. Let's team up</h2>
            <p>Tell us more about yourself and what you're got in mind.</p>

            <form action="#">
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="First Name" required>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Last Name" required>
                </div>
                <br />
                <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" required style="width:450px">
                <br /><br />
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">

                    <select required>
                        <option value="+91">+91</option>
                        <option value="+1">+1</option>
                        <option value="+44">+44</option>
                    </select>
                    <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" required style="width:365px">
                </div>
                <br />
                <textarea placeholder="Enter message" rows="5" required style="width:450px">

                </textarea><br />
                <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
                <br />
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>